HEADWORD: Subtangent
<hw>Sub*tan"gent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>
<def>The part of the axis contained between the ordinate and tangent
drawn to the same point in a curve.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

